Amanda Holden, 52, sported a bold all-red outfit as she departed the Heart FM studios in Leicester Square on Wednesday. The presenter wore flared trousers, a tight high-neck jumper, and a coat draped over her shoulders, all in the same shade of red. Amanda completed the look with matching court heels and a large handbag. She wore her blonde hair down and covered her eyes with chic black sunglasses. It come after she celebrated her 52nd birthday on February 16 with a lavish trip to Dubai with her family and friends.